args:
The duo arrive at the dunefolk settlement and
find themselves signed up as models for the
festival fashion show. But during rehearsal,
word comes of an imperial attack, so the
ladies take up arms to defend the people.
Nice, Ria! Looks like those other fiends\ntotally bailed!
Aye. Still, 'tis passing strange to find\nfiends in such a place.
As the prince said, mayhap the Empire's\nfell influence across the land yet stokes\ntheir kind to frenzy.
Yeah, it was like a battle every other day\nfor a while there, but I thought stuff was\nfinally calming down.
Well, if they're here to mess with my\nfestival, I'm going full cray-cray on 'em!
I worry for the settlement.\nLet us make haste.
Ooo, I can see it! Over there, Ria!
(So these are the heirs to my people.)
(They appear hale and happy both;\nit gladdens my heart to see such.)
NOW are you happy you came?
The blood of the Sandreach flows yet,\nand her children have hewn out a new\nfuture in this place.
To see it with mine own eyes is a blessing.
Girl, if you're happy, I'm happy.\nNow let's beeline for the party zone!
Right?! It's been a hot minute, but you\nKNOW I wasn't gonna miss the big bash!
Are you participating again this year?\nWe could really use you!
Oh, you better believe I aaaaaa...ctually,\nscratch that. Can't this year.
Why not? You did so well last year.
I know, but I super can't this year.\nGotta show my bestie around. Sorry!
Yeah, I brought a buddy this year!\nEverybody, this is Ria.
Hey there! Nice to meet you. I hope you\nhave a great time at the fest... Umm...
Sorry! I didn't mean to stare!
Er, and I hope this isn't a weird thing to\nask, but are you...?
(Marry! Is my disguise so soon undone?!)
Are you interested in modeling\nfor the fashion show?!
Yeah, see, we set up a big stage in the\nsquare for the festival, and people put on\nall these different shows.
There's singing, dancing, and music,\nbut the biggest one is the fashion show!
But wherefor... Er, but why\na fashion show?
It's tradition, I guess. Apparently our\nancestral queen had a real thing for\nclothes.
Fie, but I was never given over\nto such frippery and fandangle!
O-oh! I merely meant that a queen with\nsuch...um...mad style must have had\nfans dangling off her! Or whatever?
Mayhap the crowds she drew inspired\nthis super cool fashion show? Ha...ha?
Yeah, I dunno any of the details,\nbut I guess she's what started it.
Plus, a lot of us dunefolk are into fashion\nanyway, so we're all in regardless.
Then the invitation you extended\nto my biff Nadine just now...
Is to be a model, yeah! What do you say?\nCould be a great memory of the festival.
A memory, huh... Why didn't I think of\nthat?!
Still, I fear it a task well outside my bail...\nEr, I mean, that is totes not my...jam?\nI think Nadine should do it alone.
Aw, c'mon, Ria! You'll be a natural!
NADINE! I must protest! I do not—
Thanks a bunch! I've gotta help with setup,\nbut I'll catch you two later. Byeee!
Fie, Nadine! What have you done?!
Uh, something fun? You don't really just\nwant to stand on the sidelines and watch\nall the action, do you?
I've no experience as a model!
Aw, it's easy. I did it last year.
I'll show you everything you need to know!
Okay! So once you get to the end of the\nrunway, you turn around and vogue.
That look! It's so fierce!\nSay cheese, girl!
You shall NOT document this moment!\nWe are in training, and I will thank you\nto keep your wits about you.
Okay, but vamping is a huge part\nof being a model though.
And where better to vamp than in front of\nol' Clix here? Ka-CHACK!
Spare me your sophistry! We both know\nfull well your focus ever drifts toward the\ncapturing of those fell images!
Not true! I'm totes coaching here!
And girl, the one thing you're lacking\nright now is confidence.
I mean, I love the wistful look as much\nas the next girl, but this is a party—\nso stop fretting and just serve it UP!
And how am I to feel confident when this\nfarce was thrust upon me by your caprice?
Girl, you're a QUEEN. Confidence should\nbe, like, your thing or whatever.
You may be right, but you ask a feat\nI simply cannot muster as I am now.
Which is why you are meant to be\ninstructing me! Now, cease this\nendless dithering and—
When you were all angry just now,\nyou were a total boss—THAT'S\nthe energy you gotta bring to the catwalk!
Forsooth, but you are an irredeemable...\nHmm? Is that not one of the young\ndandiprats we spoke with afore?
What's wrong, bub? Something go\nsideways with festival prep?
Hide, both of you! Fiends are coming!
Ohmigosh, they ARE gonna mess\nwith my fest!
And not just fiends—there's a whole bunch\nof imperial troops with 'em, and they're\nall headed this way!
Oh, are you kidding me right now?!\nNo Dyrenell jerkface is gonna stop ME\nfrom stomping it out on that runway!
Runway aside, we must scatter this host.\nThe settlement's defense falls to us!
